      • processSongLog

        public int processSongLog(java.lang.String logFilename,
                 int curTime)
        Processes the song log from the given file name. The file is assumed to be in the same path as given when the parser was constructed. Returns the current time after the log is processed. For instance, if given curTime is 1 and the log contain N plays, the returned time should be N+1.
        Parameters:
        logFilename - The name of the play log
        curTime - The current time of the recommendation system
        Returns:
        The current time after importing the log
